# Instinct RPG — Proof HTML must be clickable (GitHub Pages)

When you create or reference a **design proof HTML** file (card renders, layout labs, compare pages):

## Always give Annie a live link she can click

**Base URL:** `https://elequin-sandbox.github.io/instinct-ttrpg/`

**Format:** markdown link to the deployed file — not a repo path alone.

Example:
- Good: [Ancestry Snap Check proof](https://elequin-sandbox.github.io/instinct-ttrpg/ancestry-snap-proof.html)
- Bad: `ancestry-snap-proof.html` or `/workspace/ancestry-snap-proof.html` with no URL

## Before sharing the link

1. Proof HTML lives in the **repo root** (or another path included in Pages `publish_dir: .`).
2. **Commit + push `main`** so GitHub Actions deploys to Pages.
3. Confirm deploy started (or that the file was already deployed).

## When creating new proofs

- Name: `*-proof.html` or `*-design-lab.html` in repo root.
- Self-contained CSS (proofs should render without Card Studio JS).
- In your reply, lead with the **clickable Pages URL** — file path is secondary context only.

